OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWindy and often cloudy, with
OL,6,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, these most
OL,7,Ffrequent over higher ground. Showers
OL,8,Fwill gradually become more isolated
OL,9,Fthrough the afternoon, allowing dry
OL,10,Fand bright conditions for many,
OL,11,Fparticularly in the east. Feeling cool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny remaining showers will
OL,14,Fgradually fade, with winds easing to
OL,15,Fleave a dry night with largely clear
OL,16,Fskies. Some patchy cloud may linger
OL,17,Fover the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
