PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F164A1781319819
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FGenerally fine and dry, with
OL,6,Flight winds and bright spells, though
OL,7,Foften rather cloudy. Some sunny spells
OL,8,Fmay develop through the afternoon,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east. Turning
OL,10,Fslightly warmer.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,13,Fbut increasingly cloudy on Monday,
OL,14,Fsome possible rain late. Breezy and
OL,15,Fcloudier on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,16,Fwith outbreaks of rain at times,
OL,17,Fperhaps locally heavy. Temperatures
OL,18,Fnear normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
